---
// SystemBlocks.astro
---
<section class="relative bg-slate-950 text-white py-24 overflow-hidden border-t border-slate-800">

  <div class="absolute top-[-120px] right-[-60px] w-72 h-72 bg-orange-500/30 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">

    <div class="mb-16 reveal">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold">
        Stage 1 — The Growth Website System
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400 max-w-3xl">
        A code-based website built for speed, tracking and growth.
        Not a template. Not a page-builder. A real business asset.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <div class="reveal group relative rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 hover:border-slate-600 transition">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Performance-first architecture</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-400 text-sm">
          Astro build. Optimized loading. Core Web Vitals respected
          from day one.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal group relative rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 hover:border-slate-600 transition">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Tracking done right</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-400 text-sm">
          GA4 events wired to real outcomes — calls, forms,
          bookings, purchases.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal group relative rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 hover:border-slate-600 transition">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Ownership + guarantees</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-400 text-sm">
          You own hosting, domain and code.
          Deadlines and performance backed by refunds.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="reveal mt-12 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/30 p-6 text-slate-300">
      After Stage 1, your system is ready for Stage 2 — traffic,
      SEO and scaling without rebuilding.
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
